Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 我到底還能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變那如狹隘庭園般的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.29,0:00:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還活不到人生的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗 相擁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無意識中被刻上的經驗紋身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.30,0:00:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當站在懸崖邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.47,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苦難抓住了我的手腕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看到了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往更加寬廣的領域\N往更深更大的某處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝著無法預測的世界前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.13,0:01:15.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And lt's calling me again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.84,0:01:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.13,0:17:24.54,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:29.86,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:31.30,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}我很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:34.33,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}請救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.35,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}其實我不想這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:13.75,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}我不想和你戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:17.75,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.55,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.61,0:19:04.99,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}想對你說實話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:10.79,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}還有很多話想對你說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:15.34,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.07,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.72,0:19:30.23,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}好喜歡你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:59.43,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:12.57,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.40,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}綾人君，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:28.16,*Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.15,0:01:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RehXephon出來後向北飛去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.28,0:01:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後因為有高強度磁暴發生，目前行蹤不明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在，統合自衛隊的早期預警機正在搜索中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.46,0:01:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TERRA控制台呼叫alpha v-1，確認你已經離開T-J
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.84,0:01:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是alpha v-1，現在返航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RehXephon怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.64,0:01:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他應該在我們之前就出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐，你和艾爾菲在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.07,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.57,0:02:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼他不回到我們這裡來？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.04,0:02:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體情況隨後再報告
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在山裡降落後，神名君告訴了我這個世界的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腦中一片混亂，無法立刻理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.96,0:02:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看起來應該是真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為已經消失的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有12年時差的真實世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，過去我所在的世界是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.85,0:03:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的我又算是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.64,0:03:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.06,0:03:14.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕，我很害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕從這裡看到的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是溫暖的街燈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再高一點可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.44,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}典當行不得收取18歲以下青少年的質押品以及支付質押金
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話，你可以去其他的店
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個價格也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.77,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把錢存入預付卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一半的錢是你的，算是你自己買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，付錢的是神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，這樣真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的，已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.37,0:04:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想買長途車票，可以用預付卡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.88,0:04:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.34,0:05:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我用預付卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.05,0:05:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去鹿兒島，一張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君想逃避某個人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.64,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一點我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…這是因為有人需要他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個世界上，還有人需要他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之相比，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.86,0:05:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我孤獨一人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.74,0:05:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點辦法也沒有，這讓我不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好，浩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你，是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我忘了？太無情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在裡面無法看清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.37,0:06:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是，你到了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在你應該可以看到真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.25,0:06:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道了(血的)真實的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威脅我們的生活，人類的敵人——MU族
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MU族流著藍色的血
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你遇到藍色血液的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請馬上通知政府
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒MU族！MU族是地球的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是可怕的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你用這台機器檢查過他的ID卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看他的質押品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.14,0:07:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是物證，別指望我會還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣善良的市民是不會做違法的事情的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.65,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5A大概在山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林裡或者湖底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是一個人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,髮型是否相同，有沒有帶著眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和照片上的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他買的車票是去鹿兒島的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為他會更聰明一點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.68,0:07:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把票退了可以取回錢吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.76,0:07:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.55,0:07:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他買了去鹿兒島的車票
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可能躲藏在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼，沒什麼，再見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給誰打電話呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.27,0:08:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，白蛇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.78,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給聯合統轄部發密碼消息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標偽裝成去了鹿兒島
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的目的地不明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調查還要繼續進行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.66,0:08:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…TERRA方面怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在稍微迷惑了他們的視線吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣跑下去就要磨穿鞋底了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你似乎樂在其中啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.26,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獵犬…拿出幹勁就能像狐狸那樣聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你累了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去淋浴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，我不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,景色還很不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以很清楚的看到大海
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.38,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，你聽到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.05,0:09:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？身體不舒服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈！回答我呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…沒事，稍微有些頭暈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是因為餓了的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.37,0:09:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.95,0:09:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君你決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸豬排怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想吃肉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼吃些清淡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵條不太好，烤魚嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈？果然身體不舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，那個，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些事情想和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？突然態度嚴肅起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.45,0:10:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想吃vongole
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:36.84,*note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}vongole：用西洋蛤蜊做的意大利菜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.34,0:10:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.56,0:10:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他帶著眼鏡，大體上應該是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同伴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是他的同伴我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.66,0:11:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有個年紀相仿的女孩一起下了車
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，按日付薪的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，你是覺得應該負起責任才做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的，朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道不能總是這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.68,0:11:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去思考的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.14,0:11:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我雖然不知道該怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果有時間的話我會想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.86,0:11:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天，我會用RahXephon\N把守和你的父母從東京帶出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來，我沒有關於家人的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是誰？我不是人類嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的血液才是藍色的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.88,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對可能不是人類的自己感到害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我把一切都告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:04.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣…那樣，你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道，我無法預想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的只有一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被你討厭，絕對，絕對！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.15,0:12:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要被生下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.56,0:12:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把他們逼到絕境了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.36,0:13:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘船會開到哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外國吧，歐洲呀非洲呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.87,0:13:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我直到最近還深信東京就是整個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，你有想去看看的國家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這裡的，某個地方的某個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常遙遠的，我不知道的國家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.74,0:13:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.54,0:13:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，那個，我的母親不是我真正的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.05,0:14:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然她有些冷淡，但她也有好的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.14,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信任她…但她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑我，她不是我真正的母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…為什麼要被生下來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了神名君，一無所有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.97,0:14:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5A在活動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它開始移動了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…正在以極高的速度向…飛去…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈，不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.66,0:15:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，很溫暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，那是怎麼回事？ ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.26,0:15:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dolem？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.44,0:15:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RahXephon！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5A
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了，是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為自己在東京沒有失去任何東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:18.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有必須去保護的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護你，我想保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打敗它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神名君，我有話必須要對你說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心，我一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你在這裡等我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…有很多話要和神名君你說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道更多關於神名君你的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想你更多地瞭解我的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…神名君！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會永遠等你，永遠！永遠！永遠等你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:17:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡等你，綾人！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人、綾人、綾人、綾人、綾人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要告訴他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾人君…綾人君…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了，我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護她，我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護她，我會保護她的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要保護朝比奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要讓他知道…一定要告訴他…告訴綾人君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，我要進入房間了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦你了，貳神先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被追趕的獵犬是不會馴服的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與遠方的朋友重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.77,0:23:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識藍色天空和海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.57,0:23:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集,第二十樂章
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.86,0:23:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制者的戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界飽含著聲音